<body>
    <h1>Simon Says Game</h1>
    <p>
        A simple web-based Simon Says memory game. Test your memory by repeating the color sequence as it grows with
        each level!
    </p>

    <h2>How to Play</h2>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Start the Game</strong><br>
            Click the <strong>Start Game</strong> button.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Watch the Sequence</strong><br>
            The game will flash a sequence of colored buttons.<br>
            Remember the order!
        </li>
        <li><strong>Repeat the Sequence</strong><br>
            Click the colored buttons in the same order.<br>
            Each level adds a new color to the sequence.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Game Over</strong><br>
            If you make a mistake, the game ends and shows your score.<br>
            Click <strong>Start Game</strong> to try again.
        </li>
        <li><strong>Reset</strong><br>
            Click <strong>Reset Game</strong> to restart at any time.
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Files</h2>
    <ul class="files">
        <li><code>gameindex.html</code> – Main HTML file</li>
        <li><code>gamestyle.css</code> – Styles for the game</li>
        <li><code>gamescript.js</code> – Game logic</li>
        <li><code>logo.png</code> – Game icon</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Preview</h2>
